'''Ytterbium''', in its stabilized form, was a material vital in the production of [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]].<ref name="Harvest Moon" /> In [[thermal well]]s, ytterbium was used as a stabilizer to make the [[Baradium/Legends|baradium]] in the explosive less hazardous.<ref name="Rules">''[[Rules of Engagement: The Rebel SpecForce Handbook]]''</ref> Ytterbium was found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sarrahban]] in the [[Sarrahban system/Legends|Sarrahban system]]. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] managed to extract all of Sarrahban's stabilized ytterbium during the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Invasion of Sarrahban|invasion]] of the planet.<ref name="Harvest Moon" />

